summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 5.2°C), outside temperature (up 4.0°C), and inside temperature (up 1.8°C), more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 5%), and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.1 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 3738 lux), cloud levels (up 338 m), and rainfall (up 0.1 mm).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 4569 lux), rainfall (up 0.1 mm), and cloud levels (up 481 m) when compared to today.
